1353
02:03:02,500 --> 02:03:03,900
Lady Marion.

1354
02:03:17,800 --> 02:03:20,300
Preparem-se!

1355
02:03:20,700 --> 02:03:22,300
O inimigo está chegando.

1356
02:03:23,000 --> 02:03:25,500
Defendam as posições!
Vão!

1357
02:03:25,700 --> 02:03:27,100
Rápido.

1358
02:03:52,800 --> 02:03:54,200
Sigam-me.

1359
02:04:16,400 --> 02:04:19,300
